DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260716
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260717
SUMMARY:Kettlebell Total 30 Min
DESCRIPTION:Single-bell total-body circuit. Add Golf Mobility Warmup.\n# Kettlebell Total 30 Min\n\n- Domain: `kettlebells`\n- Session Duration: `30 min`\n- Precedence: `primary`\n- Format: `AMRAP`\n- Equipment: `single kettlebell`\n\n## Summary\n\nSimple single-bell total-body circuit done without setting the bell down inside each round.\n\n## Work\n\n- 10 swings\n- 10 squats\n- 10 presses\n\n## Notes\n\n- Do one round without putting the bell down.\n- Add pull ups or push ups if desired.\n
END:VEVENT
