DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260624
SUMMARY:Kettlebell 30 Min
DESCRIPTION:Primary AMRAP circuit. After\, complete The Stack: Foundation session for swing speed. Mobility: include Hip Mobility to support recovery.\n# Kettlebell 30 Min\n\n- Domain: `kettlebells`\n- Session Duration: `30 min`\n- Precedence: `primary`\n- Format: `AMRAP`\n- Equipment: `kettlebell`\n\n## Summary\n\nSingle-kettlebell conditioning circuit with swings\, squats\, presses\, rows\, and push-ups.\n\n## Work\n\n- 10 swings\n- 5 squats\, weight on one side\n- 5 shoulder presses each side\n- 5 rows each side\n- Push ups (50% max)\n\n## Notes\n\n- Perform as many quality rounds as possible in 30 minutes.\n
END:VEVENT
